---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About — ReelClarity"
	description="ReelClarity is a small, focused tool that enhances video resolution and sharpness entirely on your device. Learn why it exists and how it works."
	canonicalPath="/about"
>
	<section class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
		<h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-[#2B2013] sm:text-4xl">
			About ReelClarity
		</h1>

		<div class="mt-6 space-y-5 text-[#5C4F3D] leading-relaxed">
			<p>
				ReelClarity does one thing: it enhances the resolution and sharpness
				of a video, entirely inside your browser. No accounts, no uploads to
				a server, no waiting in a queue.
			</p>
			<p>
				We built it as a single-purpose tool on purpose. Instead of bolting
				video enhancement onto a crowded do-everything utility site, ReelClarity
				exists to do this one job well &mdash; quickly, privately, and without
				clutter.
			</p>
			<p>
				Under the hood, ReelClarity tries to run a real on-device AI
				super-resolution model (ESRGAN) frame by frame. If your device can't
				keep up, it automatically falls back to a fast, high-quality
				resample-and-sharpen pass so you still walk away with a usable,
				enhanced file. Either way, everything happens locally &mdash; your
				video never leaves your machine.
			</p>
			<p>
				ReelClarity is part of a small family of focused, single-purpose
				browser tools built by RapidXAI.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
